summary: Idk about you but I hate it when I'm in the tag and I see post like "Axel's gf posted this on her Instagram story 😍" like...
question: Idk about you but I hate it when I'm in the tag and I see post like "Axel's gf posted this on her Instagram story 😍" like ...fans are going to steal every axel content that that girl is going to post on her own Instagram so fans can steal it and then posting that video all around inst/Twitter/tumblr like idk I don't wanna see if she posted smh about axel I don't wanna see it in the tags bc that's not what the tag is for,the same goes with maxence
answer:
Honestly love,

I’m not bothered by it. Only because I’m so used to seeing content about the actors on the tag and about the random things they do in their personal lives. Maxences ig stories, Ouba, things about the events, etc.

I, personally speaking, never see these complaints regarding any of that stuff. It’s always just when it comes to content about their gfs, or from their gfs.

If all the stuff that I mentioned about ouba and the ig lives being in the tags also bothers you, then I can understand your point a bit better. But if it doesn’t, then I don’t get the difference to be honest. Because none of that really belongs in the tag either.
